headline: Evaluating Stryker’s Valuation After New R&D Center and Siemens Partnership Boost Innovation Narrative
summary: Stryker (SYK) is drawing attention after unveiling a 140,000-square-foot research and development center in Bangalore, India. The facility is dedicated to robotics, digital health, artificial intelligence, and product security. The company also announced a partnership with Siemens Healthineers to co-develop a specialized robotic system for neurovascular procedures.
